These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Pet   | turtle  | hedgehog |
| Beverage     | tea | 7up  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, car
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, cola
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Transport    | ship      | car         |
| Beverage   | tea | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, musical
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, grey
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster   |
| Color       | grey  | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
